Iɣrm n '''Agadir Uflla''' iga yan [[Agadir (tamsdagt)|ugadir]] bahra ittawssan ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]], ila atig dar imzdaɣ n [[Agadir|Ugadir]] d iṭṭaf yan umzruy imqqurn, ɣin aɣ tn tkka tamdint taqburt n Ugadir, iḍr d gis bzzaf mur zlzal lli d izrin f tamdint ad ɣ usggwas n 1960, iga d ɣila ɣar ixrban.

== Aẓur n yism ==
Ism nns d ittawsan ddu wassaɣ n Agadir uflla, li d ikkan tutlayt taclḥit, ɛnan sis [[Agadir (tamsdagt)|agadir]] lli d illan ɣ uflla, acku illa iɣrm ad ɣ iggi yan udrar illan ɣ tuẓẓumt n lmdint, d ar itbayyan zɣ izddar zund iɣ illa ɣ uflla. Gan as yism ad n Agadir uflla. d nttat nit aɣ tusi tamdint n ugadir yism nns aylliɣ tga ɣila s yism Agadir.

== Amzruy ==
ittuyssas iɣrm ad n Agadir Uflla ɣ usggas n 1540 s ifassn n uṣulṭan Muḥammad Ccix Ssaɛdi fad ad itḥkkm ɣ imnɣi nns mgar ibrṭqqiziyn lli d israqrrn ddu udrar ɣ usggas n 1470 lliɣ tn kkan ar tllin s ubrid s [[Lhnd]]. Bnnan ɣ uftas taman yill yan ugadir ɣ udɣar nna ɣ tlla tuddurt n Funti ɣilad. d bnan ula ɣ taman udrar yan lburj yaḍn fad att sis ḍufn. Ɣayd ad yujjan Isaɛdiyn ad bnun iɣrm ɣ afa n udrar ann nit.

=== Manka s ittuybna iɣrm ===
Ittuybna iɣrm zɣ umzwaru fad ad sis mmaɣn bac ad sis ḥmun tamdint d uftas nns zɣ irumiyn d ubrrani.

* '''Asggʷas n 1505:''' Isrs-d Aqḍban abrṭqqizi Jwaw Lupiz Di Sikwira iẓṛan imzwura n ubnnu n yan lqlɛa imẓẓiyn fad ad iḥmi aɣbalu n waman mmimnin.<ref>https://www.geni.com/people/Jo%C3%A3o/6000000016531741942</ref>
* '''Asggʷas n 1511:''' Hjmn tiqbilin tisusiyin lhujum nnsn amzwaru f ibrṭqqizn lli d istaqrn ɣ ugadir.
* '''Ɣ usggʷas n 1513:''' Isɣa ugllid abrṭqqizi Manwil Amzwaru agadir ann mẓẓiyn d iga y'as s yism Santa Kruz Di Kip Di Jir ("Santa Kruz Du Kapu Di Ajwir")
* '''Asggʷas n 1536:''' Iɛln aṣulṭan alqaym bi amr llah assaɛdi s imnɣi mgal ibrṭqqizn aylliɣ yumẓ iwis Muḥammad Ccix Ssaɛdi f tamdint.
* '''Asggʷas n 1540:''' Yaɣul-d nɣ yuḍa-d Muḥammad Ccix nttan aygan amɣar anbbaḍ, ibna iɣrm, iga y'as ṣṣuṛ bac ast iḥṣn, d isḥiyyl gr 40 ar 50 mikḥala bac ad dafɛn f tamdint.

